{"tid":448144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"擁有一個香港男友此生無憾","createTime":"2017-10-26T03:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T13:37:48.000Z","uid":151558,"like":20,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ba548d110036bdcc012d6facf86c7885440a32fa","tid":448144,"uid":151558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:10:14.000Z","msg":"我date過abc、台灣仔、強國富二代 但係佢地沒一個比得上我依家嘅BB<br />\n當初我根本就沒諗過真係會同香港男仔拍拖<br />\n但係識咗佢之後我對香港男仔完全改觀<br />\n佢講嘅野有條有理有水平個人又有上進心又成熟<br />\n唔似得之前果d對象淨係識打機玩同買野又大男人<br />\n我發覺香港男仔真係會好尊重同好錫女朋友<br />\n又體貼又溫柔<br />\n紀念日仲會整手工野送俾我<br />\n煮野食又叻<br />\n每次去佢度訓都拾乾淨屋企、清乾淨廁所同浴缸、幫我準備埋生活用品<br />\n連扑野都對我好溫柔從來都係錫住我黎<br />\n真係好識照顧人"},{"pid":"4f7621177a1ec5b83585ed4203103dd4e3460791","tid":448144,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":34,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab747a8f15f497cc7848c72deed88cdd9ca96e6c","tid":448144,"uid":50744,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:13:21.000Z","msg":"恭喜巴打搵到真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767de2ab647c3c15ef132556c1b2945b4dd23a6a","tid":448144,"uid":99627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"我date過abc、台灣仔、強國富二代同香港男仔 但係佢地沒一個比得上我依家嘅BB<br />\n當初我根本就沒諗過真係會同日本男仔拍拖<br />\n但係識咗佢之後我對日本男仔完全改觀<br />\n佢講嘅野有條有理有水平個人又有上進心又成熟<br />\n唔似得之前果d對象淨係識打機玩同買野又大男人<br />\n我發覺香港男仔真係會好尊重同好錫女朋友<br />\n又體貼又溫柔<br />\n紀念日仲會整手工野送俾我<br />\n煮野食又叻<br />\n每次去佢度訓都拾乾淨屋企、清乾淨廁所同浴缸、幫我準備埋生活用品<br />\n連扑野都對我好溫柔從來都係錫住我黎<br />\n真係好識照顧人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83301314ad3880f267eddfb719a184de3ae6249e","tid":448144,"uid":118973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:14:15.000Z","msg":"屌 好多hehe <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd4920c81ca1b53c3e503d3ea314dd504bf5904","tid":448144,"uid":124899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:16:14.000Z","msg":"就係依類垃圾男造就港女"},{"pid":"43ae2c491433f7a120d6a3039b40039426beb720","tid":448144,"uid":59961,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:18:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係依類垃圾男造就港女</blockquote><br />\n對女朋友好其實好正常<br />\n不過樓主心態真係好撚港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0183b0cf7e85532e6c0c175df7ca90d3cd8f055","tid":448144,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"咁樣都叫港女？"},{"pid":"929842e8bcd7469a78734a3922ca2796894386ef","tid":448144,"uid":22938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"死hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83cd33c22c647c588f272ee8a0a94d99963e8fc","tid":448144,"uid":151558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就係依類垃圾男造就港女</blockquote><br />\n對女朋友好其實好正常<br />\n不過樓主心態真係好撚港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係得對方一個付出<br />\n我都有"},{"pid":"26e9dcfa0797cb5f7d10327e0c4e1cf64e8df73c","tid":448144,"uid":151558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係依類垃圾男造就港女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你先垃圾<br />\n唔怪得沒女啦"},{"pid":"6ad6080831f93a9b73ddcbe430e541fd288d8410","tid":448144,"uid":151558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恭喜巴打搵到真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每日都好掛住佢想食咗佢"},{"pid":"0a7264e839571e461a97b6101ce86d02734f7079","tid":448144,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"樓豬條仔咁似老婆奴"},{"pid":"c9a82d7819aee5536fda2c61764978aaa77041a6","tid":448144,"uid":151558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0